<h2 style="font-size:15pt;color:#2F5496;margin:14px 0 6px">6. Topic 定制规范</h2>

<h3 style="font-size:13pt;color:#2F5496;margin:14px 0 6px">6.1 命名规则</h3>

<pre style="background:#f5f5f5;border:1px solid #ddd;padding:12px;font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:9pt;white-space:pre-wrap">tbox/{device_id}/{direction}/{type}[/{subtype}][/{rpc_method}]</pre>

<table border="1" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;margin:8px 0">
<tr>
<th style="padding:6px 10px">段</th>
<th style="padding:6px 10px">说明</th>
<th style="padding:6px 10px">示例</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`tbox`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">固定前缀</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`tbox`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`{device_id}`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">设备唯一标识</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`TBOX-AF123456`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`{direction}`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`up` / `down` / `rpc`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`up`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`{type}`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">消息分类</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`telemetry` `diag` `gps` `log` `status` `command` `config` `ota`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`{subtype}`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">子分类（可选）</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`periodic` `event`</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`{rpc_method}`</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">RPC 方法名（仅 rpc 方向）</td>
<td style="padding:6px 10px">`get_dtc` `set_config` `remote_diag`</td>
</tr>
</table>


